{"tid":1133718,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真post 熟悉僱傭合約既麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2019-05-01T09:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T13:14:35.000Z","uid":205724,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de18ed200702cbd09a0905bd7fea3d5ef2308b79","tid":1133718,"uid":205724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"事源我屋企之前請左個工人，最近屋企岀現左啲問題，再加上個工人乜都唔識，所以趁呢個機會決定炒左個工人，但由於同個工人未完約，「根據僱傭合約的條文，勞、資雙方其中一方若不滿意對方，亦可以提前終止合約，只要給予對方一個月通知或一個月代通知金即可」<br />\n我屋企唔想俾錢所以就喺今年4月4日通知佢，諗住一個月通知就收佢皮啦。點知到今日，佢俾我阿媽發現佢特登花我屋企啲傢俬，我阿媽嬲到即刻趕左佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題黎喇：<br />\n正常個工人5月4日先走，但係我阿媽早左3日趕佢走，如果補翻呢3日人工俾個工人有無問題？ 如果有問題應該要點做？<br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位巴/絲打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bac77e85ee4254e116ca7b66af58811f20f08a8","tid":1133718,"uid":205724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9780fb208a130302343897c4259b53b385cf88f1","tid":1133718,"uid":205724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:17:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9e84d117ccd7f3f407f3238fa0a269dfb1fb33","tid":1133718,"uid":205724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:13:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb33dae79f1d5598dd4f69753e7fc229b928fed9","tid":1133718,"uid":79154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"搵返 Agency 搞喇"}]}